{"tid":2120107,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"19歲港男成立自家設計時裝品牌，創辨人:「不排除被抄襲」","createTime":"2020-07-22T12:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T17:36:49.000Z","uid":353419,"like":3,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"4201fa080a180463efa03c5d8cc5696c24f0b16e","tid":2120107,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T12:55:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>年僅19歲的林君諺（Emerson），對室內設計及繪圖工作深感興趣，中學畢業後負笈英國，現正修讀室內建築設計學士學位課程3年級。其間Emerson偶爾發現用於室內設計的軟件，也可用於簡單的衣服設計，令他萌生服裝設計的念頭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJY4GyV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJY4GyV.jpg&h=e1593407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本地服裝品牌Emerge主攻青少年市場，由網店開始，靠自家設計款式及獨特風格殺出重圍，更於上月開設實體店，成功在疫市中擴充業務，平均每月營業額逾萬元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XY5yzT8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXY5yzT8.jpg&h=5eeb3c6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「設計從來就不應局限於某一個類別，自己一向都喜歡研究不同的穿搭，若可以在室內設計發展外，同時在其他範疇上有自己設計的作品，未嘗不是一件好事！」<br />\n<br />\n去年暑假，Emerson決定創立個人品牌Emerge，透過網上銷售實現創業夢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1cpGCt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1cpGCt.png&h=691ceccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n品牌主打自家設計的日系簡單及工裝造型的穿搭，全部款式及剪裁均由Emerson親自設計，切合現今年輕人的需求。其設計結合藝術和時裝的元素，並滙聚不同國家的設計文化。此外，他更希望以小眾化的概念，讓每位客人都能夠擁有屬於自己獨一無二的衣服，不再在街上出現「撞衫撞款」的尷尬情況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Dm2thx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Dm2thx.png&h=6ccf0e39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最初，Emerson花了兩個多月時間設計3款T恤，將為人熟悉的西方藝術融入設計中試水溫。他將約300件製成品同時放在網店及朋友的店舖寄賣，結果反應熱烈，不到一星期就全部售罄。客人的支持，鼓勵了Emerson繼續設計更多不同種類的產品，由基本的T恤、衞衣、風褸、長褲，以至各類型的服飾配件如Cap帽等，全部一應俱全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dzdz3QW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDzdz3QW.png&h=7e4a155f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他又笑指：「不排除自己的原創產品會被抄襲，但這反而代表作品有人欣賞、有價值，既然不能控制別人，不如繼續努力，保持自己獨有的風格。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWMYL4i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWMYL4i.png&h=13532eef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E6qZvw8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE6qZvw8.png&h=56e64c98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"cad360050ee42bd94e33afca4116290e04c7940f","tid":2120107,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T12:56:49.000Z","msg":"黃定藍？"},{"pid":"96c3763fb76d077b7491bdbf1ad8106a93472a3f","tid":2120107,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T12:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52886ed1cc867698b7c540559cab4f3cb795b3f","tid":2120107,"uid":41368,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T12:58:08.000Z","msg":"啲衫⋯邊忽小眾化？"},{"pid":"29219c667059d7e69a23f90eba58b644bee359d1","tid":2120107,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:01:18.000Z","msg":"條女ok wor"},{"pid":"3470305294300f401eb6b3269a8ffc4553a59072","tid":2120107,"uid":278219,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"//成功在疫市中擴充業務，平均每月營業額逾萬元//"},{"pid":"2c9186f036e908ec113a5c86f1edde6225aaa9a7","tid":2120107,"uid":13504,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:21:04.000Z","msg":"d 設計咁平凡我話你抄人都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35505b65cc1ec8e67b8674638a79886ee179c906","tid":2120107,"uid":360826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:33:51.000Z","msg":"不如白tee 白褲  <br />\n<br />\n人地點抄你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97a8e543cd7fde9fd15009f50009f8d5096d547","tid":2120107,"uid":25516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco